Subject: Manually uninstall an agent
Description: Hi, there is no answer to this in the documantion - how do i manually uninstall an agent that is not communicating with the server?
What_We_Know__c:
Client wanted to uninstall the agent as it made the device to go completely offline.
Sent out the instructions along with the command but he said he did it directly from the machine.
Next_Steps__c: Client doesn't need further help and wanted to close the case.
Solution_Comment__c: Client managed to uninstall the EPP client successfully.
